"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"space semantic tokens","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"multiple"}]},{"type":"text","text":" or not, and expose them."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"title":"OUDSThemesOrange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"type":"topic"}}}